{"tid":1119998,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網紅小斯：教入住酒店前「談心」可免費 Upgrade！網民鬧：奉旨拎人著數","createTime":"2019-04-22T10:30:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T16:13:57.000Z","uid":66271,"like":4,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4bcd492cbbf4424eaf95415135a94d7ff801091e","tid":1119998,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T10:30:03.000Z","msg":"不少人出外旅遊遇上酒店可以免費 upgrade 都會十分開心，但原來免費 upgrade 竟可提早同酒店 bargain？ 專門教人如何賺取飛行里數的網紅「小斯」，最近在其「小斯」Facebook 專頁發文大教網民如何在入住酒店前與酒店「談心」（即透過 email 與酒店溝通，從而達到自己想要的目的，如：免費 upgrade 房間、提早入住等），分享自己先訂下一間最普通的標準房，再與酒店「談心」後成功 upgrade 房間至套房，更教網民如何與酒店提出要求。之不過，網民意見兩極，有人留言「求教學」，也有人卻指其行為屬貪小便宜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2330000/2331848/190422_Hotel_01_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2330000%2F2331848%2F190422_Hotel_01_600.jpg&h=d14690ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網紅「小斯」指租住的這間是<br />\n<br />\n越南新開的酒店，他指自己在網上花費約 HK$1,300 「訂咗間柴房（即一般酒店的標准房）」，之後便「膽粗粗 send email 去談心」。他稱所謂的「談心」其實已有固定的 template，email 的內容主要係了解一下酒店的特色，在 email 中表示自己是慕名而來，誇讚酒店，這樣酒店便很大機會滿足你的要求。在成功 upgrade 後，更稱「雖然間 garden suite 唔貴只係二千港紙左右，但有得 up 都勁開心啦！」又指「知唔知點解當年公開試英文科要教 Practical Skill？就係等你大個咗住酒店可以談心用啊！」 <br />\n<br />\n此分享一出後，有不少網民均留言「求教學」，並指希望網紅分享其「談心 template」，更有網民指自己要仿效一下，在下次入住酒店前先與酒店「談心」。不過，有部份網民斥此行為屬貪小便宜，「都幾 cheap , 難為你教得出」、「有 free upgrade 係 appreciate or lucky. 仲教人寫 email 嘗試去攞著數，見到多 2 張床放响到，就諗住可以屈蛇住多啲人？到底係乜道理」、「R 嘢都好曬，冇錢咪唔好 X 住囉」、「乜 X 野係『談心』即係解貪心？」、「正宗香港人心態 - 貪小便宜」、「自己 book 果陣就計到盡平幾百，到人哋 upgrade 比佢就話『雖然唔貴』」。<br />\n<br />\n此外，也有網民質疑酒店會為其升級房間，只因他的身份，「因為你係小斯啫」、「如果寫話小斯介紹，是咪都可以 upgrade 」、「唔 up 你，怕你唱」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2330000/2331848/ho01_meitu_1_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2330000%2F2331848%2Fho01_meitu_1_600.jpg&h=0bc8ce6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2330000/2331848/190422_Hotel_05_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2330000%2F2331848%2F190422_Hotel_05_600.jpg&h=d240abb5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93d3771627edcf21309c5eb19c5ec89344f9e78d","tid":1119998,"uid":17641,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T10:37:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>小斯只係一隻臭閹狗</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1cd90e1586c25e1b67943331383062cce4723fc","tid":1119998,"uid":35014,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T10:42:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9dd88008e1d81914d6930b9b92416297c1e6c56a","tid":1119998,"uid":10757,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T11:07:15.000Z","msg":"男定女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b5c2668b9f360fe4835934862ee54cee6f4ef3","tid":1119998,"uid":67043,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T11:27:47.000Z","msg":"香港人個名就係俾呢啲撚樣敗壞晒"},{"pid":"05019c96490006ca182d7420e5d5b1900d9de136","tid":1119998,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dd88008e1d81914d6930b9b92416297c1e6c56a","tid":1119998,"uid":10757,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T11:07:15.000Z","msg":"男定女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T11:28:51.000Z","msg":"前日先知佢話自己係男..."},{"pid":"e499be4638f2f63d376fa5c3dcf28a89f257d5fc","tid":1119998,"uid":41818,